ce|website=Splice|language=en|access-date=2019-06-03}}</ref>\n\n== Selected Discography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Artist\n!Album\n!Song\n!Role\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2019\n|[[Weezer]]\n|[[Van Weezer]]\n|[[The End of the Game (Weezer song)|The End Of The Game]]\n|Producer\n|-\n|[[Weezer]]\n|[[Weezer (Teal Album)|The Teal Album]]\n|[[Africa (Weezer song)|Africa]]\n|Vocal Producer\n|-\n|[[Jukebox the Ghost|Jukebox The Ghost]]\n|[[Off to the Races (Jukebox the Ghost album)|Off To The Races]]\n|[[Everybody's Lonely]]\n|Engineer\n|-\n| rowspan=\"14\" |2018\n|[[Ghost (Swedish band)|Ghost]]\n|[[Prequelle]]\n|[[Witch Image]]\n|Composer\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[(Fuck A) Silver Lining]]\n|Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[Say Amen (Saturday Night)]]\n|Composer, Additional Production, Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[Hey Look Ma, I Made It]]\n|Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[High Hopes (Panic! at the Disco song)|High Hopes]]\n|Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Dancing's Not A Crime]]\n|Additional Production, Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|One Of The Drunks\n|Additional Production, Engineer, Background Vocals\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|The Overpass\n|Composer, Additional Production, Engineer\n|-\n|[[Panic! at the Disco|Panic! At The Disco]]\n|[[Pray for the Wicked|Pray For The Wicked]]\n|[[King of the Clouds|King Of The Clouds]]\n|Composer, A